module.exports = {"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Life is a YOLO game","author":"Henry Wu"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"/home/circleci/project/src/pages/foreman-and-env-local.md absPath of file >>> MarkdownRemark","html":"<p>由於我自己會習慣寫一個簡單的 shell script 去啟動 foreman，但最近發現無論怎麼設定 foreman 都不會再去讀取  <code class=\"language-text\">.env.local</code>。GitHub 上有人回報類似的問題  <a href=\"https://github.com/bkeepers/dotenv/issues/234\">bkeepers/dotenv#234</a>，雖然主旨是 <strong><code class=\"language-text\">heroku local</code> makes it impossible to override settings from <code class=\"language-text\">.env.&lt;environment&gt;</code></strong> ，但解法也適用 foreman。</p>\n<p>解法不難，以下是原來的啟動語法。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\">\n      <pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ foreman start -f Procfile.dev</code></pre>\n      </div>\n<p>改成以下的形式，差別在於多了後面的 <code class=\"language-text\">-e .env,.env.local</code>。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\">\n      <pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ foreman start -f Procfile.dev -e .env,.env.local</code></pre>\n      </div>\n<p>由於我自己 clone 的 <a href=\"https://github.com/myceto/suspenders\"><code class=\"language-text\">suspenders</code></a> 也有另外寫一個腳本 <code class=\"language-text\">./bin/run</code> 來執行 foreman，找到解法之後我就立刻更新了。對於已經生成的專案，只要將 <code class=\"language-text\">./bin/run</code> 的內容改成以下內容即可。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\">\n      <pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token shebang important\">#!/bin/bash</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span> -f .env.local <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">then</span>\n  foreman start -f Procfile.dev --env .env,.env.local\n<span class=\"token keyword\">else</span>\n  foreman start -f Procfile.dev --env .env\n<span class=\"token keyword\">fi</span></code></pre>\n      </div>","excerpt":"由於我自己會習慣寫一個簡單的 shell script 去啟動 foreman，但最近發現無論怎麼設定 foreman 都不會再去讀取   。GitHub 上有人回報類似的問題   bkeepers/dotenv#234 ，雖然主旨是   makes it impossible…","frontmatter":{"title":"foreman 偵測不到 .env.local","date":"February 18, 2016"}}},"pathContext":{"slug":"/foreman-and-env-local/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/clean-urls-in-drupal-7/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"啟用 Drupal 7 簡潔網址時的地雷"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/activerecord-and-rows/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"ActiveRecord 與列輸出"}}}}


